1947;;While the Sun Shines;;British;;Anthony Asquith;;Barbara White, Ronald Squire;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/While_the_Sun_Shines;;Lady Elisabeth Randall is an English Air Force corporal during World War II. She is on her way to marry her fianc√© when she finds herself being romanced by two different men. The first man is Colbert, a Frenchman residing in England. The second man is Joe Mulvaney, an American lieutenant. Difficulties ensue as Randall finds that due to these romances both her military career and her impending marriage are in danger.